      "content": "To find out which of your friends have birthdays today on Facebook, follow these steps:\n\n- Open Facebook on your computer or mobile device and log in to your account.\n- On the left sidebar, click on *Events*. If you don't see Events, click on *See More*.\n- Then, click on *Birthdays*. This will show you a list of your friends' birthdays, including those who have birthdays today, recently, or upcoming \u00c2\u00b9.\n- Alternatively, on the Facebook mobile app, tap the search button (magnifying glass icon) and type \"Birthdays.\" Select *Birthdays* from the search results to view the list of birthdays \u00c2\u00b2.",
